<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV116">
<l>māṟuceyta vāḷarakka ṉāḷulappa vaṉṟilaṅkai</l>
<l>nīṟuceytu ceṉṟukoṉṟu veṉṟikoṇṭa vīraṉār</l>
<l>vēṟuceytu tammuḷeṉṉai vaittiṭāmai yālnamaṉ</l>
<l>kūṟuceytu koṇṭiṟanta kuṟṟameṇṇa vallaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Because the Warrior—who achieved victory by going to and killing</l>
<l rend="indent">the sworded Rakshasa who opposed [Him], so that [his] days were wasted</l>
<l rend="indent">turning Laṅkā into ashes on that day—</l>
<l>Did not set me inside Him as a separate [thing],</l>
<l>Can Yama part [me from Him] and count [my] past mistakes?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
